===Hardware specification=== *CPU: ''[[Qualcomm]]'' IPQ4029 @717MHz :Quad-core ARM (Cortex-A7) *Memory: 256MB (SDRAM) DDR3 *Storage: 64MB (SPI NOR) Flash *WiFi: [[Qualcomm]] IPQ4029 (802.11abgn+ac) :[[Qualcomm Atheros]] QCA9882 (802.11an/ac) *Network: 2x Gigabit Ethernet ports *Power: 12V, 1.25A via barrel or 802.3af/at PoE
